The paper discusses the generalization properties of neural networks, which is a common topic in the machine learning community. The experiments are conducted on image and natural language datasets, indicating a focus on computer vision and natural language processing. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
